{"tid":849203,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"[TG谷] 孤兒瘋人院","createTime":"2018-10-05T13:38:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-05T13:38:32.000Z","uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e625cbe2dceadaab30fc2da51203078e1bd640","tid":849203,"uid":171592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-05T13:38:32.000Z","msg":"孤兒瘋人院 <br />\n專收集一堆說話太瘋癲而被踢或者鍾意玩狼人既孤兒，隨意傾談你既所思所想,<br />\n以下人士請勿內進:<br />\n- 23歲以下人士 <br />\n- 搵食人士即踢 <br />\n- 狗公麻煩走啦 <br />\n- 娘娘行遠啲呀 <br />\n<br />\n我地谷內已有專屬狗公、娘娘、搵食人士，佢地會不斷監察，以防有人威脅到佢地既地位。 <br />\n每個月會清一次深潛人士，拒絕cdrom，大家有心想傾計先入，谷內有來自各行各業既人，想傾乜都可以，只怕你開唔到題。<br />\n <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/DzuS7EqihgnikjViGASA2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FDzuS7EqihgnikjViGASA2w&d=LVeiHdKwMKcZ54QT6wQ44TCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=e51eb608\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/DzuS7EqihgnikjViGASA2w</a>"}]}